><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ritchey2006-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ritchey2006_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Ritchey, K.D.; Goeke, J.L. (2006). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sed.sagepub.com/cgi/content/abstract/40/3/171\">\"Orton-Gillingham and Orton-Gillingham Based Reading Instruction: A Review of the Literature\"</a>. <i>The Journal of Special Education</i>. <b>40</b> (3): 171\u2013183. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1177/00224669060400030501\">10.1177/00224669060400030501</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Journal+of+Special+Education&amp;rft.atitle=Orton-Gillingham+and+Orton-Gillingham+Based+Reading+Instruction%3A+A+Review+of+the+Literature&amp;rft.volume=40&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=171-183&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1177%2F00224669060400030501&amp;rft.au=Ritchey%2C+K.D.&amp;rft.au=Goeke%2C+J.L.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fsed.sagepub.com%2Fcgi%2Fcontent%2Fabstract%2F40%2F3%2F171&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOrton-Gillingham\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ies.ed.gov/ncee/wwc/pdf/intervention_reports/wwc_ortongill_070110.pdf\">\"What Works Clearinghouse Intervention Report: Orton-Gillingham-based Strategies (Unbranded)\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. US Dept of Education. July 2010<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"now